# Single source of truth for the vLLM-Omni serving stack (recommendation: one version,
# one route, one source of truth). Sourced by deploy/run_job.sh and deploy/feasibility_omni.sh;
# pass to docker build as --build-arg VLLM_PIN/OMNI_PIN.
#
# 0.24.0/0.24.0 verified end-to-end on H100 (2026-07-15 feasibility run): model loads (150s,
# 73GB VRAM), /v1/models OK, profiler traces flush. vllm-omni >=0.22 is REQUIRED for the
# Cosmos3OmniDiffusersPipeline (no 0.24.1 exists on PyPI as of 2026-07-15).
# Keep vllm and vllm-omni major/minor in LOCKSTEP.
VLLM_PIN=0.24.0
OMNI_PIN=0.24.0
